	<description>
		Castlevania: Symphony of the Night meets Dragon Age: Origins in this choice driven dark fantasy RPG. Play as Coal, a misfit dragon who wants to be a knight. The game is primarily being created by a husband and wife game studio. Currently we're actively developing for Mac, Windows, Linux and the game will be DRM-Free. With a primary focus on Steam.
	</description>

	<histories>
		<history>
			<text>A Dragon Named Coal started with the idea of a handicaped dragon who wants to be a knight. Bullied and rejected from dragon society, he becomes a monster hunting his own kind.</text>
		</history>
		<history>
			<text>Semi-autobiography, the game draws heavily from founders Rachel and Ash Blue's experiences. Particularly growing up in broken homes and dealing with severe bullying in public schools. These themes bleed into every aspect of the game, from the design and aesthetic, to mechanics.</text>
		</history>
	</histories>

